node.text: Oh how time flies 😫 Sending big sis off to 3rd grade this morning! We’re gonna miss having you around every morning Ev! We all love you so so much! You’re the coolest 3rd grader we know😎❤️

node.text: Happy birthday handsome boy! I’m so lucky I get to spend 24-7 and the rest of my life with you! You truly are my best friend. Love that I met you when you were only 19, cause I get to watch you turn into a total smokin’ hot MAN! 😉(Swipe to see a pic from a few years ago!) I hope you feel extra special today, I love you so much!💞

node.text:
I feel so fortunate to be able to send my kids to school with lunch every day! And Ev’s fav is anything on soft and fluffy King’s Hawaiian Rolls. @KingsHawaiian is partnering with @NoKidHungry to launch “Share a post, help feed kids.” For every public social media post shared using the hashtag #KHShareOurBread, King’s Hawaiian will donate $5 to No Kid Hungry, which can help provide up to 50 meals to kids in need*! #ad 

 

🍞 🍞 🍞

 

*King’s Hawaiian will donate $5 to No Kid Hungry for every public social media post shared using #KHShareOurBread between August 15 – September 30, 2021, up to $25,000. $1 can provide up to 10 meals. Meal equivalency varies during COVID-19 relief. No Kid Hungry does not provide individual meals; your donations help support programs that feed kids. Learn more at NoKidHungry.org/OneDollar

node.text: Happy birthday to my sweet angel boy! Our first weeks together started off in the nicu.. and I promised myself I would make up for that lost time & snuggle the heck out of you the second you could come home.. and I sure did! This year was TONS of snuggles, tons of love, tons of playing, tons of smiles. You bring so much happiness to our family and we love you more than you’d ever know! Happy birthday big boy Z❤️🎉

node.text: Happy Father’s Day, @cole.labrant 💞 We all love you so much. You go above and beyond for your family & we have no idea what we would do without you. You love your kids like crazy & you’ve got this whole dad thing down to a T by now. You blew all of my expectations out of the water... I’m always so amazed by you. I love you beyond! I hope you feel special today❤️

node.text: I love this sweet girl. She radiates JOY! She is such a gift to our family. I sure do love watching her play soccer and try new things. I think activities are so good to keep kids busy and teach them important things in life. My kids could be the best or the worst at whatever they do, and I would have the same reaction. What I hope the most for my kids is that they love Jesus, love people, and bring kindness and light into everything they do. & this girl does such a great job at that already. Im so proud of your sweet heart, Posie Rayne! ❤️⚽️
